This folder contains examples how "confy" configuration loader might
be used.  This example explains *only* one source from which "confy"
can read configuration - simple modules. For examples of other
possible please take a look into documention:
https://confy.readthedocs.org/en/latest/

Contents:

- sample_email_backend: very simple and totaly fake python module just
  to be able to show "confy" lazy importing features

- settings: module that contains sample configuration and explains how
  the things are working

- run_example.py: simple script that shows how loaded configuration
  might be used